13. Selected contour lines and cliff lines digitised by ANU Fenner School from 1:100K scale topographic maping.', false, 'DEM_d8-9s', 'http://spatial.ala.org.au/geoserver/gwc/service/wms?service=wms&layers=ALA:dem-9s', NULL, '', '', '', NULL, 'http://www.ga.gov.au/meta/ANZCW0703011541.html', 'Topography', NULL, '846', '2009-03', '2008', 'eng', NULL, 'custodian', 3, 'https://www.ga.gov.au/gadds/licences/licence_1.html', NULL, 'http://www.ga.gov.au/meta/ANZCW0703011541.html');
